{"type":"message","id":"fff3ab00","parentId":"c41c90ac","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:18:12.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"进程还在运行。让我先kill它，然后直接使用sessions_spawn工具。但是我发现我的工具列表中没有sessions_spawn工具。这意味着我可能需要使用其他方式来spawn兵部和工部。\n\n让我检查一下当前可用的工具。根据我的工具列表，我有：\n- read\n- write\n- edit\n- exec\n- process\n- web_search\n- web_fetch\n- browser\n- canvas\n- message\n- image\n- pdf\n- sessions_yield\n- tts\n\n没有sessions_spawn工具。这意味着我作为尚书省的subagent，可能没有权限spawn其他agent。\n\n但是，根据任务要求，我需要\"立即spawn兵部和工部\"。这可能意味着：\n1. 我需要使用CLI命令来spawn\n2. 或者我需要直接执行开发工作\n\n让我先kill那个进程，然后检查是否可以通过CLI spawn。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6afebf01d46743d798e57b28","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"ember-shoal"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_49365880f1ec4a8cbb7b98f7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw --help | head -50","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":130,"output":216,"cacheRead":14272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774369083087}}
