{"type":"message","id":"f7aede1e","parentId":"9ad1dddc","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:18:30.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"openclaw命令似乎总是很慢。让我换一个思路：既然我是尚书省的subagent，而且我没有sessions_spawn工具，那么我应该：\n\n1. 直接开始执行开发工作\n2. 使用exec工具来创建项目和代码\n\n根据任务要求，明早06:00需要交付MVP。我现在应该立即开始开发工作，而不是等待spawn。\n\n让我采取以下策略：\n1. 我（尚书省）直接开始后端和前端开发\n2. 创建项目结构\n3. 实现核心功能\n\n时间紧迫，我需要立即行动！","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🚨 紧急决策\n\n由于openclaw CLI响应缓慢，且作为尚书省subagent我需要立即开始工作。**时间就是生命！**\n\n### 立即开始MVP开发"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2d771c63f0d747dea2169bf8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p backend frontend && ls -la","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-shangshu"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8e0811856a8949118679baea","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"warm-claw"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":266,"output":213,"cacheRead":14400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774369102665}}
