{"type":"message","id":"ecdc5e72","parentId":"66a34e80","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:18:49.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"糟糕！.NET和PostgreSQL都没有安装。这是一个重大问题。\n\n我有几个选择：\n1. 安装.NET SDK和PostgreSQL（但可能需要很长时间）\n2. 使用Docker运行PostgreSQL\n3. 使用其他技术栈（比如Node.js + Express + SQLite）\n\n考虑到时间紧迫（只有5小时30分钟），我应该选择最快的方式。让我检查一下：\n1. Docker是否可用\n2. Node.js是否可用\n3. 安装.NET需要多长时间\n\n让我先检查这些选项。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🚨 重大问题：开发环境未就绪\n\n.NET和PostgreSQL未安装！立即检查替代方案："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b8b098415f9643d894dca230","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker --version && docker ps","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e9fefd7568e8487186f1672c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node --version && npm --version","timeout":5}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4bb1135bc5614a45921d2df4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"apt-cache search dotnet | grep -E \"^dotnet-sdk\" | head -5","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":251,"output":205,"cacheRead":14976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15432,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774369118164}}
