{"type":"message","id":"9d184abe","parentId":"4ef747fa","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:19:09.191Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，情况是：\n- Docker未安装\n- Node.js已安装（v22.22.1）\n- .NET未在apt cache中\n\n这意味着我需要：\n1. 使用Node.js而不是.NET\n2. 使用SQLite或JSON文件而不是PostgreSQL\n\n这样可以大大加快开发速度，因为：\n- Node.js已经安装\n- SQLite内置在Node.js生态系统中\n- Express.js框架快速开发\n\n让我调整技术栈并立即开始：\n- 后端：Node.js + Express + SQLite + JWT\n- 前端：React（或纯HTML/JS）+ Fetch API\n\n这样可以在5小时内完成MVP。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 💡 技术栈调整（紧急应对）\n\n由于.NET和PostgreSQL未安装，**立即切换到已安装的Node.js技术栈**：\n\n### 新技术栈\n- **后端**: Node.js + Express + SQLite + JWT\n- **前端**: React + Fetch API\n- **数据库**: SQLite（内置，无需安装）\n\n### 优势\n✅ Node.js已安装（v22.22.1）\n✅ SQLite无需安装\n✅ 开发速度更快\n✅ 5小时内可完成MVP\n\n### 立即开始！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b7ae659f37654fdc99190776","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace-shangshu/backend && npm init -y","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8433191cbd774ac7bd2f9f39","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"npm install express jsonwebtoken bcryptjs cors dotenv sqlite3 uuid --save","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-shangshu/backend","timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":373,"output":331,"cacheRead":15168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15872,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774369134982}}
